ActTerritorial Lands Act
PrecisORDER RESPECTING THE WITHDRAWAL FROM DISPOSAL OF CERTAIN LANDS IN THE NORTHWEST TERRITORIES TS'UDE NILINE TU'EYETA (RAMPARTS RIVER AND WETLANDS) - which provides the withdrawal from disposal the surface and subsurface rights of certain lands (approximately 14,700 square kilometres), in order to facilitate the establishment of the Ts'ude niline Tu'eyeta (Ramparts River and Wetlands), in the Northwest Territories, as a candidate protected area, through the N.W.T. Protected Areas Strategy.
